latestPosts.caption: I almost forgot that this was the whole point ✨❤️

Took a trip with complete strangers, and somehow, it turned into one of the best experiences of my life. ✨ 

Bir Billing wasn’t just about the views or the adventure, it was about stepping out of my comfort zone, making unexpected connections, and truly living in the moment.

For the first time, I felt like I was in my own Yeh Jawaani Hai Deewani story, new people, crazy fun, and that feeling of being alive and free.

Would you ever take a solo trip with strangers? Because honestly, I can’t wait to do it all over again. 
Thanks to @bokettotravels for making this experience an amazing one #corememories 🤍 

#BirBilling #solotraveldiaries
